# .dev.vars — Local development secrets for Cloudflare Workers
# Copy this file to .dev.vars and fill in the values.
# .dev.vars is gitignored and should NEVER be committed.
#
# In production, set these via:
#   wrangler secret put <KEY>

# Optional: Email API key for sending real magic links in production
# In dev, magic links are printed to the wrangler console instead.
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Optional: A secret used to sign session tokens (if you add HMAC later)
# SESSION_SECRET=change_me_to_a_random_32_char_string
